            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600">
                <p>E-Greeting was founded in 2020 with a simple mission: to help people connect meaningfully in a digital world. Our founders, a team of designers and developers, noticed that while digital communication was becoming more prevalent, it was also becoming less personal.</p>

                <p>Traditional greeting cards have always been a way to show someone you care enough to select something special just for them. We wanted to bring that same thoughtfulness to digital greetings, combining the convenience of digital delivery with the personal touch of a carefully chosen card.</p>

                <p>What started as a small collection of holiday templates has grown into a comprehensive platform offering hundreds of designs for every occasion, from birthdays and anniversaries to congratulations and thank you notes.</p>

                <p>Today, E-Greeting serves thousands of users worldwide, helping them stay connected with friends, family, and colleagues through beautifully designed, personalized digital greetings.</p>
            </div>

