                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Our Vision</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">To create a world where digital communication is as thoughtful and meaningful as traditional greeting cards, helping people maintain strong connections regardless of distance.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
